Biography

The Hon Rosalind Maud Cubitt was born on 11 August 1921 at 16 Grosvenor Street in London, England. Her parents were Roland Calvert Cubitt and Sonia Rosemary Keppel.[1][2][3]

Marriage and family

On 2 January 1946 she married Major Bruce Shand in London.[4][3]

Bruce and Rosalind had three children: Camilla Rosemary Shand, Sonia Annabelle and Mark Roland.[3]

Death and burial

Rosalind died on 14 July 1944.[5][3]

She was buried in Holy Trinity Churchyard, Stourpaine, Dorset.[1]
